    <div class="our-story-big-leagues-left">
      <p>Long story short, our original flavors were not only a big hit with friends and family, but we were lucky enough to gain fans across the country.</p>
      <p>What better way to keep up with demand than to grow our operation to the great hardworking city of Detroit. Duke’s has the best of both worlds, pairing our creative Rocky Mountain heritage with a city known for it’s work ethic and craftsmanship.</p>
      {{ 'our-story-big-leagues-01.jpg' | asset_url | img_tag }}
    </div>
    <div class="our-story-big-leagues-right">
      {{ 'our-story-big-leagues-02.jpg' | asset_url | img_tag }}
